                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On April 4, 1952, President Truman issued Executive Order 10338 entitled
                    “Coordination Procedures Under Section 507 of the Mutual Security Act of 1951.”
                    This Order was identical, save for <pb facs="0524" n="498" xml:id="pg_498"/>
                    minor technical changes, to the Draft Executive Order, with handwritten changes,
                        <ref target="#pg_494">page 494</ref>. The text of Executive Order 10338 is
                    in 17 <hi rend="italic">Federal Register</hi> 3009.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
